comments: Doncic (DAL) extends his left leg and intentionally kicks the ball.
O'Neale (BKN) and Kleber (DAL) engage and disengage during the rebound, and marginal contact occurs.
Finney-Smith (DAL) initiates contact to Durant?s (BKN) left arm, which affects his upward shooting motion for the jump shot attempt.
Simmons (BKN) and Kleber (DAL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Duke Jr. (BKN) dislodges Hardaway Jr. (DAL) from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to secure the ball.
Watanabe (BKN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith?s (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kleber (DAL) turns to roll and incidental contact occurs with O'Neale (BKN) as O'Neale goes under the pick.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a defensive goaltending by Durant (BKN) is overturned and BKN is given possession of the ball.
Simmons (BKN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith?s (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Doncic (DAL) brings his off-arm toward O'Neale (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as Doncic releases away without applying any force.
Kleber (DAL) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in O'Neale?s (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs during the pick.
Durant (BKN) gathers the pass on his left foot and takes two steps before his shot at the basket.
Simmons (BKN) is moving alongside Doncic?s (DAL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in Simmons?s (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Doncic (DAL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes one step before releasing the pass.
O'Neale (BKN) avoids making contact with Bullock (DAL) during his contest on the jump shot attempt.
Watanabe (BKN) brings his hand toward Doncic?s (DAL) path and marginal contact occurs during Doncic?s drive.
Kleber (DAL) initiates contact with Durant?s (BKN) left arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) cleanly deflects the ball OOB.
Kleber (DAL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Durant?s (BKN) right arm.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Claxton (BKN) both make a play for the loose ball, and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Doncic (DAL) moves slightly toward Irving (BKN) during the driving shot attempt, and Irving moves through the marginal contact to score.
Simmons (BKN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Bullock (DAL).
O'Neale (BKN) touches the ball last before it goes OOB.
Durant (BKN) commits a take foul on Finney-Smith (DAL).
DAL calls and is rewarded a timeout prior to Doncic (DAL) exhausting five seconds from his inbound opportunity.
Durant (BKN) initiates contact with Finney-Smith?s (DAL) left arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Simmons (BKN) releases the in-bounds pass within five seconds.
Bullock (DAL) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
O'Neale (BKN) commits a take foul on Bullock (DAL).
Claxton (BKN) establishes himself in Finney-Smith?s (DAL) path before turning his hip and delivering illegal contact that affects Finney-Smith?s (DAL) ability to defend.
